item.title: Crime in Los Angeles
item.description: We investigate the Crime in LA. We do Exploratory Data analysis on various topics such as the Month of Crime ,Day of Crime,Time of Crime. We also explore how the Crimes are related to the Sex and Age of the Victims, Crime Types, Crime Types of persons aged 70 and above. We explore on the Crimes at different Premises,Types of Crimes at different Premises,victim Descent Analysis and an analysis of Weapons used in Crime.
